item.content:encoded:
Nana DIY Dress & Cake is a casual simulation game. First, dye the jumpsuit with the color you like. You can choose a solid color or tie-dye. Then spray the skirt with a special pattern. A beautiful skirt is ready, put it on and try it on! Now that the clothes are done, let’s start making the cake!
PCMouse click and drag to playMobileTap and slide to play
